Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:18.40,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:48.89,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(270,270)}Ep. 47 - Dad's Decision
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:06.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:11.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Try to get some sleep.\NThe fever will subside this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:12.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:18.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even I, who is knows to be so rarely ill,\Nsuddenly developed a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:26.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I made up my mind to go see the Princeton Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But only dad and Lucy could accept the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:44.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They must be serving some marvelous dishes there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm hungry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like the fever subsided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:19.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. More importantly,\Nplease consider what I proposed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:20.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:23.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My farm is in a dire need of a man such as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:27.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To be perfectly frank, if I leave that farm as it is now,\NI would eventually have to give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:30.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But if you lend us your strength,\Nit'll be put back in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, please let me think about it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to receiving your reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:38.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, come visit us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:42.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious, come soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:45.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even if your dad is busy,\Nyou can come on your own, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:46.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:47.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:50.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't I bring along someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:51.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:54.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My big sister Kate really wanted to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But she's ill today...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:59.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Of course.\NNext time, be sure to bring Kate along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:02.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, taking them home, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:26.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You changed your mind\Nabout working at the mine, didn't you, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you're going to go work at the mine, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:34.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Princeton said he'd like you\Nto lend him your strength, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:38.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That'd mean I have to work on his farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:43.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:47.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I think it's way better than working at the mine.
Comment: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:47.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:49.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Isn't that right, did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:53.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a minute of silence.\NI need to think about many things at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're crossing the Adelaide Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:25.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Returned, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? I thought you'd be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've just woken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:32.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So? How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:36.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I had a meal a little while ago\Nand the fever is not very strong anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:37.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:40.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So hey, what were you doing at the Princeton's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:43.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad was talking to Mr. Princeton.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I was talking to Mrs. Princeton.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:47.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:49.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We also had lunch with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:50.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:55.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right. Their cat Prospero still remembered me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And what were you talking about\Nwith that gorgeous Madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:59.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:03.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,About me, about things that happened\Nsince our arrival to Southern Australia, about family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:08.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, during my time\Nin their house, I didn't have my memory with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:11.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So we couldn't discuss that kinda thing back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:15.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Princeton was very delighted,\Nno matter what we were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:17.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you talk about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:18.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:23.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I told her that though we argue a lot,\Nyou're the best big sister one could wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:27.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good to know. I thought you'd just\Nshower me with slander.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:30.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She said I should come play around\Ntogether with you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:32.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:37.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to play around in their house,\NI'd also rather go there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:38.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:39.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:42.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NWhat's there to be afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:45.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:51.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She's a very kind and a amiable person,\Nbut I'm a little scared of her when we're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:58.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Lucy, do you like this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:00.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's so beautiful and big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:06.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if you stayed in this house\Nfrom now on and forever, I'd be the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:13.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And how is that scary? Didn't you know\NMrs. Princeton dotes on you a great deal before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I did know, but it goes beyond that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, you're such an adorable girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:24.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to become my child.
Comment: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me back my Emily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:36.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We've done talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll join you in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a little too tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:50.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:55.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help suddenly feeling\Nlike you're Emily who lost memory again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:05.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This girl called Emily was Mrs. Princeton's daughter,\Nisn't that what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:08.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And then, she also called me that for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:12.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So the one Mrs. Princeton loved\Nwas not Lucy, but Emily?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:17.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Considering you didn't have your memory back then,\Nyou were lucky to get even that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:21.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're feeling a bit lost\Nnow that you've returned to being Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:23.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"A bit" doesn't make it justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:27.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, why don't you just become\NPrincetons' daughter and be done with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You might as well change your name to Emily too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:29.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,K...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:30.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding! Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:36.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't joke about that kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My home is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:40.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens,\NI'm Lucy-May Popple!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:44.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like Mr. Princeton is really, really rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:47.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. One look at his mansion\Nis enough to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:52.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, he's one of the co-owners\Nof the mine I'm to work at.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:57.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, honey. In the end, you elected\Nto work at a farm, rather than at a mine, didn't you?
Comment: 0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know how reluctant you are to take that offer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I want a farm of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:07.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've had my share of working at others' farms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:11.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But this time you won't be working\Nunder someone else's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:13.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be free to decide for yourself what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:19.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton holds in great respect\Nmy drive to build a farm in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:23.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's still another man\Nin charge of the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:26.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And there's no telling whether or not\Nhe'd listen to my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:31.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because of that man\Nthat things aren't going great on Princeton's Farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:32.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:35.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If so, why won't you make that farm manager stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:39.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's something for Mr. Princeton to decide.\NI can't have a hand in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:43.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But say, let's suppose that man\Nends up listening to your advice, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Would you still rather work in a mine even then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:51.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I reject the farm offer,\NI won't be able to work in the mine either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:56.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, farm it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We should start preparing to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:09:59.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:04.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've considered things thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:11.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not working on another's farm. Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:12.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:15.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another,\NI'll have to raise money with some other job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:18.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You've been quite stubborn recently, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:35.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that, Little!\NFunny is sleeping. You'll wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:42.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! He woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:49.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You must be awfully bored inside this box.\NSo, how about we take you outside, Funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that too, Little!\NYou're scaring the life out of Funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:15.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There, take a look!\NHe's running away scared now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Funny! Funny, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:20.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You can't walk on the field! Get out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go there either! Little, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Funny is heading to the front!\NPlease catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Funny!
Comment: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:46.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:53.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Whoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:55.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A wombat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:05.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, we've ran over a wombat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:09.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A wombat? I see. But there's nothing wrong\Nwith the carriage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good, then hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:12.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:36.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:41.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we shouldn't have rescued him from that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:51.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, to get ran over by a carriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lucy. I know how much you love animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:13:00.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But from now on, try to leave the wildlife\Nalone as much as you can, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:04.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not all animals are happy with being kept by people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:50.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about, John? So suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:54.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara just told me.\NYou gave your permission to us getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:55.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:14:01.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Then, I think, it's best that we decide\Non the day of the wedding ceremony as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:02.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:06.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, your whole family\Nis moving to live near the mine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we should get married before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:09.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're not moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We've changed our mind about moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Then, you're going to the mine alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:21.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No. For various reasons, I changed my mind\Non the whole "working in a mine" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:22.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:24.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:27.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you don't have to hurry so much\Nwith the wedding ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:36.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see now. So you've decided against the mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:37.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:45.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But regardless, thank you very much\Nfor approving our marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:00.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:05.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Funny died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:08.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The wombat we caught yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, it died?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:14.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He ran out to the street\Nand got ran over by Mr. Pettywell's carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:17.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a very unfortunate thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:19.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, did John come already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:20.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, father,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:26.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,if you're going to work on Princeton's Farm\Nyou'd have to move anyway, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:32.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Popple, so we need to hurry\Nwith settling on a date for the ceremony, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:37.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that. For the nearest time,\NI'm not planning to work at Princeton's Farm either.
Comment: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:38.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:42.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But why? It really felt like\Nhe made you some great offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I said too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:48.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I also don't understand\Nwhy you can't work at his farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:51.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to work on a farm\Nran by someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:55.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to run my own farm, on my own land,\Nno matter how small.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, you have the last word, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:03.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I think I'll go see Mr. Princeton\Nto give him my refusal tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:07.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go have dinner now.\NJohn, I've prepared a portion for you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:18.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:32.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, are you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:37.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've spend this whole day sleeping,\Nso I don't feel one bit sleepy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:40.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere was somehow strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:41.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At the dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:47.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone ate in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:50.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And what did they decide\Non Clara and John's wedding ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't discuss that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:56.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like everyone is displeased with dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:58.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Myself included.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:03.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton put great faith in dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:06.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But dad said he would only work on his own farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:09.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems like dad is turning it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:13.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it totally looks like a great offer!\NDon't you think so too, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:14.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:17.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But dad has a mind of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:22.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, because you're still a child,\Nyou don't understand grown-ups well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:27.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If dad made up his mind to turn it down,\Nwe can't have a say in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what'll happen to us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:40.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If Clara and John get married,\Nthey'll be happy, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:50.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:15.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come. This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:20.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, you'd give me your answer today, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:22.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:25.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I cannot accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:29.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean...\Nyou don't want to work on the farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:35.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. After a long consideration,\NI concluded that I'll have to refuse, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If so, are you saying you'd like to work at the mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:43.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now I really can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:47.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As far as I'm aware,\Nyou're currently looking for a job, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:48.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:50.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find some better job, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:51.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:53.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:58.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that by working at another's farm\NI wouldn't be able to govern my own decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not 100% true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:06.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In order to put the farm straight, we would heed strongly to your advice - that's what I'm offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I made up my mind already.
Comment: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:10.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:11.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I'm sorry to say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:20.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate deeply your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:24.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You were my best bet, Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:28.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But in this case, I have no choice,\Nbut to sell that farm away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I hope you excuse me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Pettywell has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:59.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He says he needs to meet you by all means, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:01.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pettywell, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:07.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost as though Mr. Pettywell was waiting for you to refuse, to come and grab the farm for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:08.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pettywell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:10.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:12.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:15.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He's about as apt in business\Nas he is nasty in personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:19.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He got wind of that farm not doing well somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,and had been doggedly pestering me\Nto sell it to him for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pettywell, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:28.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Up to now, I've been flatly refusing his persistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But today, finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is Mr. Pettywell doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:39.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Presently, I told him master\Nis still conversing with his previous visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So he's waiting for the latter's departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:46.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, tell him Mr. Popple is leaving\Nand bring Mr. Pettywell here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:49.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:50.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:54.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I changed my mind, Mr. Princeton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Will you work at that farm, Mr. Popple?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:02.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Though I can't if I'd be able to do much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:05.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm sure, with your help, we'll manage, Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:08.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I believe in,\Nas long as we heed to your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:12.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Mr. Pettywell to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:15.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be busy with my current visitor for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:16.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:20.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please be seated, Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:25.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to explain to you\Nthe situation on my farm in more detail now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:29.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but before that, let's have a toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:39.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I'll remember this!\NAnd I'll make him pay for it, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ouch! Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:21:58.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:00.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, welcome back, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:02.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, you stink of alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:03.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You've drunk quite a lot, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:05.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:08.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I also noticed your unsteady gait\Nwhen I saw you from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:11.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, didn't you promise not to drink anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:12.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:13.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:16.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:17.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:21.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Clara, don't you think we gotta invite John soon\Nto make arrangements on your wedding ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:24.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.40,0:22:41.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen closely, everyone.\NDad wants to tell us all something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:48.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I accepted the offer\Nof working at Princeton's Farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:49.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:53.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth,\NI was actually planning to turn it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:22:56.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But in unexpected turn of events,\NI suddenly had a change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:23:01.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, I always dreamed\Nabout owning my own farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.05,0:23:02.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But now I've come to think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:07.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,that as long as they follow my advice in managing\Nthe agriculture, working on another's farm is fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:09.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll all be moving to live on the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:14.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And the day after tomorrow, Mr. Princeton\Nwill show us around the farm. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:18.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:30.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a school at Princeton's Farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:33.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not at the farm itself,\Nbut in the nearby city of Gawler.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:35.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Though it's a little far to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:38.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so there is a school...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:43.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Though Lucy is noticeably disappointed,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.64,0:23:48.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I really feel that tonight's dinner\Nis the first happy one in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:05.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "Becoming a Well-Off Child..."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:06.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.47,0:24:09.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,366)}The Alps Story: My Annette
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.43,0:24:13.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next show - The Alps Story: My Annette.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.10,0:24:14.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It starts in the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.96,0:24:16.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it, okay?
